ActUnited Nations Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Regulations Implementing the United Nations Resolutions on the Central African Republic
PrecisRegulations amending the REGULATIONS IMPLEMENTING THE UNITED NATIONS RESOLUTIONS ON THE CENTRAL AFRICAN REPUBLIC in order to (1) fulfill Canada's international legal obligation to implement the binding decisions of the Security Council set out in Resolutions 2399 (2018), 2488 (2019), and 2507 (2020); and (2) address miscellaneous amendments requested by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
